Why they are vendored here
--------------------------
Originally this repo told followers to copy these files live from the upstream
repo. Upstream drifted, and a fresh checkout could pair a `deepseek_v2.py` that
imports `fused_indexer_q_rope_quant` with a `sparse_attn_indexer.py` that no
longer exports it, producing an ImportError at model load (repo issue #5).

To make the recipe reproducible we pin a KNOWN-GOOD, MATCHED set here — the exact
files that serve GLM-5.2 in production on our 4x DGX Spark cluster. In particular
`sparse_attn_indexer.py` DOES export `fused_indexer_q_rope_quant`, which
`deepseek_v2.py` imports. Do not overwrite these with a fresh upstream pull
unless you re-verify the pair.

No functional modifications were made to these files versus the upstream copies
we deployed; they are redistributed verbatim for reproducibility.

